Output demo/benchmark.mp4

Set Width 1000
Set Height 750
Set FontSize 14
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Sleep 500ms

Type "# NemoClaw: Memory Benchmark — Flat vs Typed Index"
Enter
Sleep 1500ms

Type "node demo/benchmark-demo.mjs"
Enter

Sleep 25s
